issue.title: Finish text mode video API
issue.body:
We need a few more functions added to the video API:
- [ ] print function for hexidecimals
- [ ] read from video buffer to string
- [ ] recognition of escape characters in printing functions

And some to work with the keyboard class:
- [ ] ability to select text
- [ ] copy and paste mechanism
